Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:21.41,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I think of me and you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:21.41,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,Đôi khi tớ nghĩ về cậu và tớ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:26.59,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,And every now and then I think
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:26.59,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,Và bây giờ lúc này tớ cũng đang nghĩ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.54,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never make it true
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.54,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,Chúng ta sẽ chẳng thể vượt qua
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:33.56,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,We go through some crazy times
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:33.56,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,vượt qua những lúc giận dữ khó kiềm chế
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:39.88,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,And everytime I wonder if I'll be losing you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:39.88,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,và lúc nào tớ cũng tự hỏi liệu tớ mất ấy thì sao ??
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:41.88,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:41.88,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,Sẽ chẳng bao giờ đâu nhỉ :)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:47.02,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my friend you give me a reason
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:47.02,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,Bạn tớ ơi, hãy cho tớ một lý do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:50.53,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,To keep me here believin'
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:50.53,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,để khiến tớ thêm vững tin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:57.19,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,That we'll always be together this way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:57.19,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,Rằng tớ và ấy sẽ luôn bên nhau trên con đường khó khăn này
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:01:00.90,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know my friend you give me a reason
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:01:00.90,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,Và cũng hãy cho tớ một lý do
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:03.09,Boy,,0000,0000,0000,,To make me stay
